# Late Arriving Facts

## Definition
Fact records arriving after expected processing period.

## Difference
Late Fact -> delayed transaction
Late Dimension -> missing dimension first

## Common Solutions
- Backdated loading
- Recalculate aggregates
- Watermark delay

